description.narrative: This activity (TCI Technical Assistance) is a component of Technical Assistance Project for Non-Aided 'At Risk' Caribbean Overseas Territories reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £3,677,494. This component benefits Turks and Caicos Islands, and works in the following sector(s): Public finance management (PFM). , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, Crown Agents Limited, Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office, Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 19-08-2010 and the end date is 31-12-2013.
